\i\b\fs22 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\i0\fs24 \cf0 Page 19:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\b0 \cf4 Robert Thomson\'92s efforts writing and collecting for the LCS songs \'96 discussed in Chapter 2\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\b \cf0 Page 19:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\b0 \cf4 a period when radical discourse was largely concerned with a split between the represented and the unrepresented, between a narrow identification of the political nation with the elite and a broader idea of \'91the people\'92\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

