\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\b0 \cf4 Gerrald became a flamboyant hero of the struggle in 1793; his fate \'96 transportation to Botany Bay and an early death \'96 made him a print celebrity to the radical societies in 1794\'965 and beyond\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
